IMMEDIATE
No.55/1/1/71-CF
COVENMENT OF IN DIA (EHARAT SARK AR)
CABIN ET SECRETARI AT (M AN TRIMAN DAL SACHIVALAYA
Department of Cabinet Affairs (Man triman dal Karya Vibhag)
N ew Delhi, the 18 th June, 1971.
28 th Jyaistha, 1893.
The undersigned is directed to state that the President
has been pleased to appoint the Prime Minister (Pradhan Mantri)
as Minister of Electronics (Electronics Mantri) also with effect
from June 17, 1971.
(R.N. Kalia)
for Cabinet Seoretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary/Adviser/Joint Secretary/
Private Secretary to the Prime Minister (Pradhan Mantri).
Copy forwarded for information to Seoretary to the Presid ent/
the Secretary to the Vice-President.
igha
(R.N. Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission/Secretary, Union
Public Service Commission/Comptroller and Auditor General of
India/Member-Secre tary, Pay Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries, Departments etc., of the
Government of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat/
Establishment Officer, Department of Personnel (Karmik vibhag),
for information,
(R.N. Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
*R.K.Khattar*
